title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Pau Vergó's St. Anthony of Padua, c1495, features tempura and tooled gold on wood.” [From TWA Ambassador, April 1985. Submitted by Bernard and Masha Schweitzer, Los Angeles.]
